riors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/3/02 1:42:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4543.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Questions about weapons</span><hr size=1> What's going on everyone! Ive been looking around at upgrades for my weapons and im trying to figure out which would work best. I currently use a black blade of tormenting in main hand and venom axe in offhand. In my bag i also carry a bloodpoint and a goranga spiked club. Im now lvl 46 so my blade or tormenting procs and it generates more aggro then than the goranga club. Should I go ahead and just sell the bloodpoint? Ive been thinking about picking up a bloodfire. Anyone know how this thing is for holding aggro. I would love to pick up a frosty but i dont have 7k laying around. Even if i did it would most likely go toward armor upgrades. <br>
Any suggestions?<br>
<br>
Tongpo <br>
<br>
